Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}縱線是日月流轉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨著季節變遷  染上天空的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}橫線乃人之生計
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}腳踏實地  心緒搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的人民夜以繼日不斷編制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在他們那長達數百年的生命中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還玩的話就干不完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  瑪琪亞也來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下來呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用去管這個瘋丫頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遠離人類  為織布而生的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是被這樣稱呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「離別的一族」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼事了?拉欣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞下次一定要跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不能這樣粗暴的對待布哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸嘿嘿  對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊  濕成這個樣子了都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸  採到不錯的花了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊  感覺能浸出濃郁的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  明天見!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這線…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼在哭呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一個人? 即使我在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的  長老大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可真是個愛哭鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們被稱作「離別的一族」的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表幾乎不會變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能活過長久歲月的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對於不是這樣的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是像傳說一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就在幾百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的存在還是隨處可見的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像鳥一樣擁有翅膀的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在夜明前歌唱的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巨大的魚在水路上搬運貨物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些都與這個世界告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們才不斷編織希比歐之布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要還在這裡  你就不是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在歲月裡  那些不經意間淡忘的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希比歐會替我們記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不得不做出告別的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也在希比歐之中與你一同落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與我…一起落淚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果從這個伊歐夫出去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在外面的世界  遇到了邂逅的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以愛上任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛上的話  就會變成真正的孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明邂逅了  卻會變成孤單一人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「離別的一族」被強加的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安  瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天份的希比歐  可不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盛開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼說  是梅薩蒂?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去通知長老大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特是全副武裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快保護希比歐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吼哦  真是跟傳聞一樣  都是些小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  你呀  這種不是  你的菜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}退下!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索爾師團長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個村子的村長在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傳聞看起來是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但其實是超過400歲的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的生活  就是編制布匹  編織歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僅僅是這樣單調的往復而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並無意與你們有此番交集…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}能決定這件事的並不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請你們與我同行  前往梅薩蒂的王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要靠近拉欣大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把女人抓起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敢反抗的人  就地處決!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙也染上了紅眼病…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要管它  現在優先伊歐夫!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放我出去! 放我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  瑪琪亞也過來呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下來呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬰…嬰兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所謂的淚酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要有點鹽分才算能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是長老那裡的瑪琪亞嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我是來買希比歐的  但在這裡也沒辦法前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}流浪者的村子  好像被賊人洗劫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且這邊的  才剛死不久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親這東西  可真是偉大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是死了  也要守護自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過  就這樣放著不管  馬上也能在天上再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子的希比歐  就在這裡結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼點…真是連布都稱不上的一段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過  比起一個人的話  還是好不少的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的孤單一人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱得… 好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別了吧  別了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打算帶走他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可不是玩具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是我的希比歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孤單一人邂逅了孤身一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太陽公公的味道
Comment: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}【在離別的早晨裝點上約定之花】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,400,0,,{\blur3}明明是我疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.60,Default,,300,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格  德雷爾  別給我偷懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哼哼  來追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的  兩個搗蛋鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?歐諾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房  找…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小孩子撫養一個小孩子肯定是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個  是你的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的話  就算看起來這樣  年齡也分不清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格  德雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我… 我才15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子… 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子的名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的嬰兒!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是女孩的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙  不是男孩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那… 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞… 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  好啦好啦  可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我親戚的孩子  還會織布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}店後面有個很久不用的織布機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是伊歐夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是瞞不過塔雷爾你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的布可以賣很高價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼好的搖錢樹的身份就算問我我也不會說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒是你本來就很吃緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要帶個伊歐夫的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來會發生什麼誰也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管那孩子在不在都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你  這是這週的份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以來真是感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀  你家的起司  乍一嘗就和別家不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡哪裡… 下週也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再一嘗果然就是不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下下週也拜託您了  呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是這樣的阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也會覺得一個女人要把孩子養大很難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你懂了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家的老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被患了紅眼病的雷納特給殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又不懂了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親到底意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有母親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種啊  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真棒啊  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀  真是變得像一個媽媽了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我像… 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈哈  怎麼會有這麼不可靠的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們幾個  山羊棚打掃完了嘛!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好  是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走  德雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}汪汪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過來  給我把屁股撅起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來叫一聲  媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不… 不算
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才的不算!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽——媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說一次呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.84,0:23:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊—嗚—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又有一頭雷納特的紅眼病發病了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立刻進行了處決
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骨骸在隔離後焚燒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後埋到地底深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還活著的個體還剩5頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊… 這是何等的悲慘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至今為止  梅薩蒂能壓制周邊各國
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.36,0:23:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠的就是能在天空飛翔的古獸  雷納特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是雷納特死光了  總有一天平衡會被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了維持梅薩蒂的權威
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定需要有能代替雷納特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超越了人類的東西的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被選中的血統!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索爾  那女孩怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個要成為黑澤爾王子的妃子的伊歐夫女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們明明擁有著翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不從這裡飛走?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因為你們會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把各種感情裝在心中燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.21,0:24:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最終連身體也燒為焦炭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後就那樣死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.28,0:24:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人  王傳喚您
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.76,0:24:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人  為什麼一直來這邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為很像希比歐的塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.87,0:24:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.37,0:25:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它表達含義了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 「歐諾爾 打起精神啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出生的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.32,0:25:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會編制布匹來代替文字傳達心情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.96,0:25:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽出生的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.02,0:25:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出生的地方在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.95,0:25:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.86,0:25:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔的媽媽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.80,0:25:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說媽媽和大家都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.14,0:25:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾出生的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.82,0:25:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是用肚子說話的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.10,0:25:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.71,0:25:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了喲! 我撓我撓我撓~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.42,0:25:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}歐諾爾才是用肚子說話的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.00,0:25:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歐諾爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要溫柔的給它披上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.65,0:25:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了啊  歐諾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.32,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歐諾爾從爸爸媽媽結婚時就在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說如果是人類的話  已經算是90多歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的媽媽  很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.81,0:26:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總是躡手躡腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.11,0:26:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.00,0:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.00,0:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs35}註：這裡使用的是僕，有點小孩子氣的自稱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還自稱僕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.49,0:26:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像小小孩一樣  真是幼稚!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.94,0:26:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的明明是艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.85,0:26:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.44,0:26:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡媽媽的男人真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.24,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪呢! 僕…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.50,0:26:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我… 討厭!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.49,0:26:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.93,0:26:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜歡我媽欸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.53,0:26:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你給我閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最討厭蒂塔了!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.65,0:26:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧? 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.71,0:27:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.09,0:27:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.38,0:27:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給  這個月的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.35,0:27:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了  可以幫我看一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有個客人帶了一匹希比歐來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.08,0:27:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.13,0:27:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.01,0:27:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.84,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂的主城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.84,0:27:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與王子聯姻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.84,0:27:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.63,0:27:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.09,0:27:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.75,0:27:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}塔雷爾說能讓你乘上運貨船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以幫你通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.08,0:27:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看  那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.25,0:27:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也差不多  正好是個契機也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.92,0:28:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  艾瑞爾怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶著孩子踏上長途旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.87,0:28:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可比你想像的還要艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且  有隱情的話更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾放在我這看顧也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.78,0:28:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.24,0:28:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.52,0:28:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.81,0:28:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥  埋得太深的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.56,0:28:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.63,0:28:36.60,Default,,400,0,0,,{\blur3}要是  歐諾爾活過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.11,0:28:36.57,Default,,0,500,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}淺的話  會被野狗挖出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.96,0:28:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.81,0:28:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蓋上土的話  就見不到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.10,0:29:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來這裡的話  隨時都能見到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.17,0:29:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蓋上土的話  就不能一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好的誇誇它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.81,0:29:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼痛苦  就去往來生了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家  早晚這一天都會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.42,0:29:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歐諾爾只是生來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.38,0:29:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就注定了這一天來得會比我們早
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.18,0:29:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.04,0:29:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.16,0:29:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  稍微去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.63,0:29:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.12,0:29:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都會死嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.50,0:29:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.52,0:29:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也會?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.51,0:29:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等  等一下啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.53,0:29:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾會…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.84,0:29:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都會  比我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.05,0:29:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更早的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.59,0:30:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更早更早的迎來那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.76,0:30:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.49,0:30:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.61,0:30:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.54,0:30:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}順序什麼的怎麼樣都無所謂的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.71,0:30:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格也會!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.20,0:30:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是  艾瑞爾的媽媽啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.10,0:30:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽是不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.82,0:30:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家的媽媽就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.69,0:30:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽肯定都是不會哭的!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.80,0:30:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.03,0:30:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.94,0:30:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.32,0:30:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.34,0:30:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.30,0:30:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.14,0:30:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.59,0:31:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.21,0:31:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這等著我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.57,0:31:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好的睡到床上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.18,0:31:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是變重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.25,0:31:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然  是太陽公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.03,0:31:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭了  我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.62,0:31:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我是艾瑞爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.53,0:31:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這以後  也會一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.05,0:31:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.49,0:31:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.04,0:31:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.54,0:31:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.22,0:31:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.16,0:31:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.42,0:31:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的話  已經不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.28,0:32:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不去送送他們  這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.97,0:32:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想去外面!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.26,0:32:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等  不可以的!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.39,0:32:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.03,0:32:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的  不是跟我說好了嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好的做個乖小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.51,0:32:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.10,0:32:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你活著啊  瑪琪亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.47,0:32:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還活著… 克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.41,0:32:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:32:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盯上了伊歐夫長命的血統
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.93,0:33:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會襲擊村子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.26,0:33:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶走蕾莉亞也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.34,0:33:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽  蕾莉亞是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.16,0:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你讓他喊媽媽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.04,0:33:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.06,0:33:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是讓他喊  這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.21,0:33:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊… 我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒有在責備你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.17,0:33:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是  長老大人一直在說的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.19,0:33:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  我沒有忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.80,0:33:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.51,0:33:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.81,0:33:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.17,0:34:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天早晨  會舉行慶祝王子結婚的遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.13,0:34:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從王宮出發的王子的隊列
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.69,0:34:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會為了與從行宮出來的蕾莉亞的隊列匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.85,0:34:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}度過這座橋
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就在這裡  襲擊王子乘坐的雷納特
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.26,0:34:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}引起騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.63,0:34:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁著行宮警備變輕的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.96,0:34:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}將蕾莉亞奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.80,0:34:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遊行  我也要看
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯… 抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.77,0:34:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.60,0:34:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.66,0:34:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.15,0:34:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽  一到這裡  就變得不像媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.81,0:34:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.37,0:34:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.96,0:34:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.23,0:34:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我撓  我撓  我撓  我撓~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.03,0:34:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我撓  我撓  我撓  我撓~
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.89,0:35:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了今天這個好日子準備的紀念品有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.97,0:35:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們已經把伊歐夫的血統召入王室了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.75,0:35:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特和伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.18,0:35:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}流傳在現世的古老傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.42,0:35:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩者都已經被我們得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被神選中的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.33,0:35:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以說敵人已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.82,0:35:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之後  通過黑澤爾王子和蕾莉亞公主的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.79,0:36:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的傳說將會誕生於梅薩蒂!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.57,0:37:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.02,0:37:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是暗殺者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.09,0:37:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.08,0:37:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞  蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.05,0:37:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.41,0:38:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.26,0:38:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.28,0:38:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.10,0:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.24,0:38:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.80,0:38:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都在等著蕾莉亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.28,0:38:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.49,0:38:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經  不能走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.45,0:38:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.83,0:38:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.12,0:38:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.25,0:38:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞你很靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.13,0:38:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是的  城堡的高牆你也能飛過去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.53,0:38:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經無法再見克里姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.06,0:38:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.89,0:38:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走  瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.34,0:38:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.17,0:38:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.43,0:39:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.46,0:39:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係  我能飛過去對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別讓她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.05,0:39:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}追
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.42,0:39:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.69,0:39:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果對她出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.10,0:39:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以飛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.81,0:39:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬰兒長大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.04,0:39:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果還活著的話  應該有六歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.73,0:40:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣? 外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.56,0:40:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有一半是而已
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.39,0:40:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉欣…長老她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.99,0:40:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼把伊歐夫的外出作為村子的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.98,0:40:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因為她知道  來到陸地上的伊歐夫之後的命運將會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算本人不希望這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.96,0:40:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為和其他人不同  會被他人用怪異的目光看待  被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到最後會被厭惡  直到被排除
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.38,0:40:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「離別的一族」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.54,0:40:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都在面對著「離別」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.81,0:40:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.28,0:40:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微享受一下正常的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.53,0:41:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆  你的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.55,0:41:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少先把上衣脫掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.61,0:41:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬰兒…是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.76,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.97,0:41:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為母親…是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.77,0:41:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  可以算作母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.22,0:41:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.82,0:41:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米多會教給我  會幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.45,0:41:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像弟弟一樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.49,0:41:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  還是有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.46,0:41:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要艾瑞爾笑起來  我就非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.10,0:41:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.50,0:41:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我在艾瑞爾身旁  能讓他充滿笑容的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:41:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就會一直在…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.55,0:42:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.20,0:42:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明艾瑞爾會先死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.37,0:42:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明艾瑞爾會讓瑪琪亞你孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.37,0:42:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別把她弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.55,0:42:19.77,Default,,0,700,0,,{\blur3}不是的  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.25,0:42:22.00,Default,,200,0,0,,{\blur3}不要弄哭媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.84,0:42:20.76,Default,,0,600,0,,{\blur3}克里姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.02,0:42:23.86,Default,,0,700,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  住手 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.64,0:42:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能保護她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.56,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能…保護重要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.88,0:42:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會留在梅薩蒂  救出蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.51,0:42:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有孩子的你  會成為我們的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.18,0:43:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以…瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.33,0:43:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.37,0:43:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.83,0:43:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們回不了家了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.50,0:43:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.63,0:43:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩人去新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.51,0:43:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的地方是…米多和蘭格哥哥都不在的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.76,0:43:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.16,0:43:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能和大家說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.71,0:43:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  只要媽媽在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.90,0:43:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.14,0:43:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽也是  只要艾瑞爾在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.15,0:43:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.78,0:43:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有隱情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.65,0:43:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是一發生問題就馬上甩手逃跑  我可受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.22,0:43:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.13,0:43:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.36,0:43:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  你給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.41,0:43:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.37,0:43:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽再去周圍看看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.13,0:44:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這客房裡先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.20,0:44:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.27,0:44:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等著  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.92,0:44:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.78,0:44:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們這裡主要是做酒的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.42,0:44:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般都是深夜工作  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深夜是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.36,0:44:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.98,0:44:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有孩子…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.24,0:44:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他還很小
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.22,0:44:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.07,0:44:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前辭掉的那個人就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.97,0:44:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼年輕  真是什麼也不考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.45,0:44:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.63,0:44:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼不是?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.65,0:44:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有作為母親的自覺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.16,0:44:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.63,0:44:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我這裡沒有能交給你這種人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.30,0:45:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.53,0:45:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.97,0:45:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽我說  我把希比歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別給我增加工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.49,0:45:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.80,0:45:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼擅自拿出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.62,0:45:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  你看啊  媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.20,0:45:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不聽我的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.72,0:45:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.07,0:45:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…剛剛就給我搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找不到工作的話  甚至飯都吃不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.69,0:45:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.81,0:45:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼讓我為難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.01,0:45:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.53,0:45:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我撓  我撓  我撓
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.02,0:45:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚餐我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.17,0:46:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.68,0:46:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…不是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.35,0:46:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親的自覺什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.89,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.35,0:46:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僅僅是…在模仿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.96,0:46:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是米多這樣告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.65,0:46:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能愛上任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦愛上的話  就真的會變得孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.19,0:46:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的…一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.49,0:46:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.73,0:46:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.63,0:47:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.92,0:47:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.09,0:47:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡…你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.37,0:47:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.19,0:47:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.06,0:47:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.50,0:47:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.40,0:47:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.93,0:47:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.27,0:47:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定以為那是我蛻下來的殼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛻下來的殼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.95,0:47:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.04,0:47:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:47:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.20,0:47:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.38,0:48:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣 一直長不大該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.38,0:48:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.12,0:48:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.73,0:48:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不長大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.53,0:48:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就不能保護媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.65,0:48:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽又在哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.70,0:48:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.55,0:48:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我可是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.95,0:48:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.79,0:48:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾也約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.28,0:48:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.67,0:48:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要保護媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.89,0:49:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好  慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.68,0:49:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快來  已經做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.56,0:49:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.18,0:49:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.64,0:49:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦  我要把之前的欠債一併還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.20,0:49:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊  找到女人了就一直炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.32,0:49:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才沒說呢  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.83,0:49:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個角度的話只能靠經驗記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.94,0:49:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以叫你別做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.60,0:49:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我之前還覺得挺順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.27,0:50:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.89,0:50:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  三瓶凱爾啤
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.21,0:50:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的  馬上到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.46,0:50:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊的也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.80,0:50:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.95,0:50:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這小姐有副不錯的美臀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.38,0:50:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.86,0:50:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但真是長得不像啊  這兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.63,0:50:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.79,0:50:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們倆來這裡已經快一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.84,0:50:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.66,0:50:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有傳聞說你們倆並不是姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.52,0:50:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的原因可能是私奔出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.62,0:50:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.20,0:50:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.74,0:50:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.17,0:50:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.01,0:50:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又來新的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.37,0:50:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底要來幾個監視才滿足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.47,0:50:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟  這是鋼鐵的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.17,0:51:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多虧了梅薩蒂一直在造大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.84,0:51:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們才得以吃上飽飯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.89,0:51:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來  有點反常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.82,0:51:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是想發動戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.42,0:51:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個呆瓜王子能指揮軍隊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.42,0:51:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.65,0:51:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從來都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.70,0:51:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼吵  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.42,0:51:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天就從這裡面選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.20,0:51:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.72,0:51:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.52,0:51:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是瑪琪亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.96,0:52:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.45,0:52:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.92,0:52:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格變了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.92,0:52:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼長得那麼高了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.20,0:52:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別把人說得像小麥一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.69,0:52:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.86,0:52:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.88,0:52:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是蘭格啊  蘭格哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是艾瑞爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.96,0:52:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.91,0:52:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來打擾真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.52,0:52:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係  房間挺亂的  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.69,0:52:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.24,0:52:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米多和德雷爾也挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.38,0:52:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.40,0:52:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是景氣的地方只有像多萊爾那樣的大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.94,0:52:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄉下的話到處都在衰退
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.85,0:52:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷爾也出了村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.21,0:52:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.62,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷爾也在找工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.74,0:52:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為不找的話就活不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.24,0:52:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.45,0:52:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和女孩子約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.58,0:53:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是  我有夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.15,0:53:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.50,0:53:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會給你準備點吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.85,0:53:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.80,0:53:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到這邊以後  他就開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.97,0:53:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常拚命地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.19,0:53:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.85,0:53:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟沒辦法出售希比歐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.61,0:53:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且因為我的原因  不能在一個地方呆太長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.93,0:53:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.66,0:53:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟沒有血緣關係的事  他已經知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.36,0:53:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.79,0:53:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大約五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.84,0:53:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我說要分開睡的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.33,0:53:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始不再叫我「媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.23,0:53:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是「喂」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.60,0:53:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「來一下」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.61,0:54:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全是像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.97,0:54:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他正處於這個年紀吧  我也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.78,0:54:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說  蘭格
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.07,0:54:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道蕾莉亞現在怎麼樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.41,0:54:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.77,0:54:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把骨頭也充分地燒掉  灰埋到地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.28,0:54:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.64,0:54:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係的  梅德梅爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.21,0:54:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個  父親大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.05,0:54:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黑澤爾大人很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.13,0:54:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.61,0:54:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.42,0:54:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.36,0:54:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如同曉月一般的髮色  瞳孔中浮現金色的環
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.41,0:54:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有被認為是伊歐夫人民的特徵的低體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.15,0:55:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是梅德梅爾大人的身體並沒有這些徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.92,0:55:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.07,0:55:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又沒能生下長孫  又不能讓後代繼承長命的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.78,0:55:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個怪物還有什麼存在的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.67,0:55:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾大人降生後  她再懷孕也會很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.77,0:55:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黑澤爾大人好像也對蕾莉亞大人感到膩煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.79,0:55:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可憐的黑澤爾
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.69,0:55:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少再找個新的女人給他
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.83,0:55:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.58,0:55:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之後會把伊歐夫的倖存者找出來  作為新的代孕
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.40,0:55:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.42,0:55:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.96,0:55:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果沒有這些亂七八糟的裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.67,0:55:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果對我已經沒有興趣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.02,0:55:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就把我給扔掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.08,0:55:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.29,0:55:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.97,0:55:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷納特已經死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.27,0:55:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.40,0:56:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從我生下梅德梅爾以後
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.47,0:56:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就被一直關在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.14,0:56:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不能和她見面
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.54,0:56:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.57,0:56:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和雷納特也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.51,0:56:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僅存在於傳說中的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.97,0:56:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曖昧不明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.45,0:56:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飛向天空的一族也是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.05,0:56:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜明前歌唱的花朵也是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.32,0:56:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明在這個世界上活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.62,0:56:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反抗應該是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.10,0:56:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了尋找留下傳說的這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.22,0:56:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.91,0:56:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是你把這個傳說…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.86,0:56:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給滅殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.61,0:57:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請讓我  贖罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.13,0:57:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.52,0:57:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼就讓我和梅德梅爾見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.15,0:57:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不讓我們見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.88,0:57:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我生的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.00,0:57:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經…連她的味道都忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.21,0:57:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱起她的時候  那柔軟的感覺也…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.99,0:57:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.78,0:57:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們要從我這裡剝奪多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.86,0:57:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就那麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.50,0:57:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想讓我孤身一人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.07,0:57:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果見不到梅德梅爾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.77,0:57:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就把瑪琪亞給帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.37,0:57:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.10,0:57:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把身為伊歐夫的瑪琪亞給…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.66,0:57:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.36,0:57:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}受不了孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.62,0:58:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打掃得很周到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.97,0:58:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們一直不都只是兩個人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.27,0:58:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前也沒有客人來過我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.44,0:58:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  稍微來一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.30,0:58:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.17,0:58:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.05,0:58:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊  這是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.61,0:58:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.01,0:58:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你做完了  稍微耽誤點時間可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.92,0:58:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.57,0:58:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  但是還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.85,0:58:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我慢慢喝著等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.34,0:58:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  去送一下貨
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.24,0:58:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.73,0:59:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是你的女人  我才注意著點的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.26,0:59:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.03,0:59:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好男人的話天下到處都是  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.32,0:59:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然被那小子占了去
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.52,0:59:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人才不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.10,0:59:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.66,0:59:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總覺得你好陰沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.69,0:59:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來  快喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.99,0:59:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已經不是小孩了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.20,0:59:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.31,0:59:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼  這個你也能喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.76,0:59:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了  你要成為大人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.33,0:59:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦  哦  哦  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.38,0:59:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起來  敲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.30,0:59:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃起來  敲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.33,0:59:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一二  一二
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.24,0:59:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一二  一二
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.20,0:59:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.99,0:59:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.26,0:59:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那再來一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.20,0:59:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.08,0:59:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在找我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.17,1:00:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個城市也已經沒辦法再待下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.54,1:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要和我一起回農場去？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.12,1:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.81,1:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.30,1:00:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山羊奶也漲價了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.64,1:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾也一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.60,1:00:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.39,1:00:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.90,1:00:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果要是牽連到米多和德雷爾
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.22,1:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 希望你能給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.94,1:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從小時候開始我就想要成為瑪琪亞的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.95,1:00:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你能考慮一下  以後的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.75,1:00:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個  還有和我的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.10,1:01:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得沒有辦法  好好考慮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.59,1:01:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為至今為止我只想著艾瑞爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.98,1:01:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如何才能和艾瑞爾一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.16,1:01:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如何才能變的像一個真正的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.54,1:01:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是完全  完全找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.94,1:01:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在還是找不到一點頭緒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.58,1:01:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我腦子很笨
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.43,1:01:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今後也想一直只想著艾瑞爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.72,1:01:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.25,1:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尋找接下來的住處  還有找工作的話
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.00,1:01:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我也一起幫忙找吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.30,1:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要一個人全部承擔啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.50,1:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.19,1:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.97,1:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一股酒臭味
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.84,1:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.99,1:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是什麼我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.74,1:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼了艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.77,1:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.25,1:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明以前都一定會做的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.98,1:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.62,1:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.15,1:03:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們被看作是私奔過來的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.80,1:03:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說是你要被新的男人給搶走了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.73,1:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.41,1:03:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.29,1:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.56,1:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要睡的話就去床上
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.15,1:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能走嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.77,1:03:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可以踩!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.16,1:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個不還是艾瑞爾織給我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.69,1:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是讓人厭煩
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.30,1:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼還保存著這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.48,1:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直把我當個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.70,1:04:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠都不會變的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.72,1:04:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.52,1:04:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.93,1:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說啊  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們又得搬一次家了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.36,1:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一次搬去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.47,1:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的話去哪裡都好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.72,1:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要是和艾瑞爾一起的話
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.89,1:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才沒把你當作母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.81,1:05:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能請你幫我疏通一下關係  幫我當城堡的士兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.28,1:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.47,1:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞會傷心的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.78,1:05:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她又不是我的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.04,1:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.19,1:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你跟她說了這句話嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.94,1:05:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.87,1:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是用什麼樣的心情  懷著什麼樣的想法才把你養大的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.81,1:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別天真了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.53,1:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在和你差不多的年紀的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.45,1:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞就努力想要成為一個母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.19,1:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.10,1:06:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是  我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.08,1:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼  那個人會…如此地珍視我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.74,1:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.24,1:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.03,1:06:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了我而拚命
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.40,1:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直以為這種人就是母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.62,1:06:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才叫她母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.61,1:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.04,1:06:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是  現在的我沒有辦法保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反而會傷害她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.32,1:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我發現了自己的這種感情
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.92,1:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我沒辦法保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.53,1:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這樣嗚嗚哭的樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.28,1:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和嬰兒的時候完全沒變
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.51,1:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.81,1:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了  我自己來
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.33,1:07:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也要離開城市的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.73,1:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等看著艾瑞爾離開之後再走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.15,1:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小心點  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.06,1:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路順風
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.81,1:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出發了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.22,1:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.66,1:08:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能哭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.36,1:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.96,1:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙子  艾瑞爾  明明約好了要保護我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.49,1:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.00,1:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.50,1:10:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛  我還以為能看到真正的雷納特呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.99,1:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.57,1:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然以前還有很多
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.37,1:10:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但現在城裡只剩一頭了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.62,1:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和這種紙糊的玩具雷納特走在一塊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.49,1:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒辦法提高戰意吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.58,1:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你聽說了嗎  拜耶拉得到了伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.15,1:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜耶拉?真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.46,1:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}師團長閣下  能不能不要烤蝨子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.68,1:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煩人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.04,1:11:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格師團長閣下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.96,1:11:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  正在尋找
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.66,1:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說是和蕾莉亞王妃年紀相仿的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.32,1:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還不一定就是瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.25,1:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.23,1:11:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個人很堅強
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.15,1:11:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果告訴瑪琪亞  她一定會高興吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.46,1:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一直擔心著「自己能不能保護好艾瑞爾」
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.20,1:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便如此還是拚命地努力著
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.88,1:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了讓你認同她是堅強可靠的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.59,1:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.80,1:11:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或許還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.39,1:11:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我很快就要當父親了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.65,1:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂  紙糊的國家
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.15,1:12:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}將遠古的力量化為權力來褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.43,1:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是多麼地愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.52,1:12:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會不惜餘力地幫助你
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.19,1:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.09,1:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於做好準備了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.68,1:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭髮長長了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.76,1:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的頭髮必須等生下孩子才能留長超過腰部
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.36,1:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來  瑪琪亞  去迎接蕾莉亞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.62,1:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要打仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.80,1:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛苦的只有一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.50,1:13:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且你這幾年已經承受了在這之上的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.63,1:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離開伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.24,1:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失去了得到的所有東西
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.99,1:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彷彿死了一般生活在地窖的深處
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.82,1:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  你終於理解我們的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.13,1:13:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都四散各地  長老也已經死了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.31,1:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們失去了一切  非常地痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.86,1:13:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這期間
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.69,1:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你一個人非常地幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.34,1:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊歐夫的人民要一起編織同一塊布
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.31,1:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和蕾莉亞還有瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.79,1:13:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三個人擁有不同的過去是不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜你  瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.36,1:14:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來只屬於你的過去就消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.69,1:14:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們能繼續編織同一個未來了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.14,1:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.54,1:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.59,1:14:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天回來的真早啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.99,1:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼重要的時候還這麼忙  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.82,1:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離入盆還有一段時間
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.06,1:14:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯  但是我擔心你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.30,1:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我馬上做晚餐
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.16,1:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.77,1:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要勉強  我來做
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.77,1:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微活動一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.81,1:15:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啦  快坐下快坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.96,1:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於快了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.41,1:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.46,1:15:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了找工作來到梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.05,1:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和艾瑞爾再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.66,1:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.35,1:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.49,1:15:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}選我真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.03,1:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.46,1:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是拜耶拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.85,1:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止是拜耶拉的船
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.15,1:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有尤格  安德拉也是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.63,1:16:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.40,1:16:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你保護好肚子裡的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.04,1:16:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太慢了  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.31,1:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.29,1:16:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收到消息說拜耶拉的部隊已經翻過了山嶺
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.10,1:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.59,1:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.71,1:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂為了鞏固自己的力量而利用了遠古之力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.64,1:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這反而使得為了懲治惡用遠古之力的梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.09,1:17:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鄰近國家結成了聯盟
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.46,1:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大臣在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.59,1:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說已經和他的部下一起出城了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.03,1:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要拋棄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.26,1:17:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多麼讓人心痛啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.83,1:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已經完了  永別了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.98,1:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陛下  請您快點
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.14,1:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  梅德梅爾大人怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.29,1:17:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是讓人忌諱的名字  不需要那種東西
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.17,1:18:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和她媽一起  全都丟下就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.71,1:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞  快走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.96,1:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.73,1:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.50,1:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.05,1:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.56,1:20:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克…克里姆 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.06,1:20:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.26,1:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是  看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.42,1:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡靈嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.00,1:20:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.90,1:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這之後
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.64,1:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要讓那些使你痛苦的人受到更甚於你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.17,1:20:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後將一切都消去
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.03,1:20:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.32,1:20:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想見見  我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.67,1:20:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.82,1:20:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不是你被逼迫生下的  不被期望的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.36,1:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是是我生下她的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.66,1:20:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可以忘了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.43,1:20:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的希比歐上沒有刻下女兒的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.90,1:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我以為克里姆和大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.79,1:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以為我失去了全部
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.93,1:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以  只考慮著女兒的事情活到了現在
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.74,1:21:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要見見那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.97,1:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要抱緊那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.26,1:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只靠這份感情活到了現在
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.99,1:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.83,1:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的梅德梅爾
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.69,1:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了  蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.00,1:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起在這裡結束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.93,1:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.49,1:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我再也不會
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.86,1:22:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓其他人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.16,1:22:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玷汙
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.02,1:22:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的希比歐了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.41,1:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.16,1:22:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.62,1:23:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.10,1:23:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞也是  瑪琪亞也是  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.97,1:23:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼  時間會向前流逝啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.09,1:24:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像是那一天一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.28,1:24:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.04,1:24:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}師團長閣下
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.95,1:24:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有情報說拜耶拉那邊有一對伊歐夫的少年和少女
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.83,1:24:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你  遇到他們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.14,1:24:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.08,1:24:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就不用了  這裡交給我們  去找瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.17,1:24:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.52,1:25:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你對梅薩蒂非常忠誠嗎  不是的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.52,1:25:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不過是為了逃避瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.39,1:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.80,1:25:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}的確  我最開始是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.17,1:25:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是現在  我有蒂塔  有伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.05,1:25:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有即將出生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.93,1:25:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這梅薩蒂是我離開那個人才建立起的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.63,1:25:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要守護它
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.79,1:25:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.32,1:25:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.02,1:25:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醫生!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.42,1:25:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.69,1:25:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.41,1:25:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.54,1:26:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.42,1:26:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開火!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.79,1:26:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開火!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.03,1:26:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.67,1:26:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油  馬上就能見到孩子了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.95,1:27:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對對  很好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.59,1:27:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔  再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.59,1:27:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.59,1:27:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.62,1:27:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要膽怯!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.56,1:27:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.91,1:27:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.59,1:27:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好怕  好怕
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.44,1:27:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救我
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.13,1:27:41.42,Default,,400,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.90,1:27:45.86,Default,,0,600,0,,{\blur3}孩子  救救孩子!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.64,1:27:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.99,1:27:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.82,1:27:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天就快亮了  攻進去!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.78,1:28:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看  孩子也在努力地想要誕生呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.23,1:28:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔和艾瑞爾就要為人父母了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.92,1:28:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是辛苦呢 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.29,1:28:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.33,1:29:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算帶他走嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.87,1:29:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他可不是玩具…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.85,1:29:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.46,1:29:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是我的希比歐
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.83,1:29:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.16,1:29:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.34,1:29:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  差不多該回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.92,1:29:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.84,1:29:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.11,1:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凍成這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.16,1:29:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.88,1:30:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.43,1:30:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.31,1:30:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是夢…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.04,1:30:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是夢哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.53,1:30:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是  雪…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.60,1:30:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是雪  是炮灰
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.90,1:30:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾和蒂塔的孩子出生了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.36,1:30:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別勉強
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.15,1:30:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別擔心  他們在等著艾瑞爾呢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.46,1:30:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩個人一直會等著你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.83,1:30:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  也是那樣從媽媽這裡出生的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.60,1:31:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的媽媽  緊緊地抱著你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.30,1:31:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手指緊緊地護住你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.96,1:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很難扳開
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.11,1:31:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一根… 一根…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.98,1:31:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.99,1:31:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒辦法成為艾瑞爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.46,1:31:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要說了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.89,1:31:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.37,1:31:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要溫柔  要堅強  要努力
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.78,1:31:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要對他人懷有愛意
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.94,1:31:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考慮艾瑞爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.03,1:31:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和考慮我的事情是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.01,1:31:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還記得我剛見到艾瑞爾的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.46,1:32:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你陪著我一起哭
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.33,1:32:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就覺得你是我的希比歐
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.19,1:32:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要和艾瑞爾在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.54,1:32:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各種悲傷  苦痛  都會被撫慰
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.48,1:32:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我卻從你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.88,1:32:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾並沒有撒謊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.66,1:32:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你遵守了約定
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.93,1:32:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直守護著我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.28,1:32:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你分開  我變成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.88,1:32:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}變得搞不懂自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.70,1:32:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算如此  只要想起你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.89,1:32:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能找回自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.86,1:32:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你呼喚著我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.69,1:32:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算叫的不是「媽媽」
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.90,1:33:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是什麼稱呼  那就是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.46,1:33:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是艾瑞爾編織出了現在的我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.28,1:33:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.53,1:33:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.26,1:33:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能幫我把艾瑞爾帶過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.21,1:33:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶到蒂塔和他們的孩子那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.45,1:33:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那裡是他的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.56,1:33:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.93,1:34:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.90,1:34:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.18,1:35:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差不多該下去了  梅德梅爾公主
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.60,1:35:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父親他們呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.23,1:35:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.40,1:35:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從這裡下去  就會迎來全然不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.23,1:35:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是就算如此 我也…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.80,1:35:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.34,1:35:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.50,1:36:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…我的母親大人
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.58,1:36:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是伊歐夫的蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.17,1:36:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}潑辣又嬌蠻
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.38,1:36:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巾幗不讓鬚眉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.94,1:36:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且  我很自由
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.40,1:36:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞  飛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.74,1:36:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我  可以飛
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.26,1:36:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親大人!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.90,1:37:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瑪琪亞
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.29,1:37:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊  你也飛起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.77,1:37:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.49,1:37:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.84,1:37:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也會忘記
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.94,1:37:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}城堡中的生活和這個早晨
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.99,1:37:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會把它們寫入希比歐
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.07,1:37:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.70,1:37:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在長久的記憶中忘卻
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.12,1:37:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會忘記
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.95,1:37:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯  只是稍微的開綻而已
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.67,1:37:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.84,1:37:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.86,1:37:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的母親大人  真是無比美麗啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.95,1:38:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅爾公主
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.26,1:38:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷納特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.07,1:38:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉亞大人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.46,1:38:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不需要什麼雷納特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.66,1:38:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不需要什麼伊歐夫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.76,1:38:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若古老的生物們的消逝是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.33,1:38:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那最後只需要遵循他們的心意
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.40,1:38:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別哭了  蕾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.43,1:38:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係  因為我一定不會忘卻
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.65,1:38:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好難過
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.92,1:39:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又難過  又痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.50,1:39:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但卻又如此美麗的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.02,1:39:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫人如何忘卻
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.92,1:39:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.24,1:39:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回來了…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.45,1:39:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.26,1:39:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.48,1:40:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好軟  軟到讓人有點怕
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.75,1:40:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得給她取個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.28,1:40:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.09,1:40:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.74,1:40:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.57,1:40:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說過「喜歡自己的媽媽 多奇怪啊」
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.00,1:40:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.44,1:40:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的媽媽那麼漂亮 那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.20,1:40:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.05,1:40:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才這孩子也是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.44,1:40:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.63,1:40:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是…可是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.03,1:41:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直嫉妒著艾瑞爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.29,1:41:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽養育成人的我愛上了你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.17,1:41:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這孩子也一定會和誰邂逅
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.74,1:41:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起把他養大吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.89,1:41:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和蒂塔  我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.47,1:41:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把將來也會愛上誰的這孩子養大
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.08,1:41:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「離別的一族」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.25,1:41:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}目睹了無數的離別
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.26,1:41:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也目睹了斗轉星移
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.40,1:41:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時光永不停滯地流逝
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.60,1:41:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因如此  才會再次邂逅
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.05,1:41:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}邂逅之後  編織出新的故事
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.62,1:42:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.58,1:42:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帶我到你爺爺那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.51,1:42:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爺爺?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.81,1:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.51,1:42:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這孩子怎麼跑到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.02,1:42:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.10,1:42:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我媽媽三年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.30,1:42:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們是非常恩愛的夫婦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.88,1:42:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅薩蒂陷落之後
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.92,1:42:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蘭格先生帶他回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.78,1:42:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然歷經磨難  但我覺得那也是幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.65,1:42:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.05,1:42:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們經常提到你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.45,1:42:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帶著一臉的幸福樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.89,1:43:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能趕上太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.35,1:43:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸他已經…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.67,1:43:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.23,1:43:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.72,1:43:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真厲害  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.47,1:43:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你努力地…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.29,1:44:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}堅持著活到了現在呢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.54,1:44:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.21,1:44:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會哭哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.16,1:44:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們約好了的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.79,1:44:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.47,1:44:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.23,1:45:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心  艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.32,1:45:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚餐之前要回來哦…
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.36,1:45:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}送給你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.20,1:45:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.15,1:46:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.89,1:46:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.17,1:46:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽我說  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.83,1:46:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.69,1:46:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.85,1:46:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上當了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.83,1:46:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定以為那是我蛻下來的殼吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.85,1:46:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出生的地方在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.42,1:46:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}癢癢蟲來了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.25,1:46:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.94,1:46:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽和大家都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.44,1:46:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}媽媽  快看快看  快看嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.79,1:46:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.42,1:46:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.37,1:46:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一到這裡  媽媽就變得不像媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.83,1:46:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要弄哭媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.51,1:46:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只要有媽媽在就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.54,1:46:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要保護媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.98,1:46:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.67,1:46:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.33,1:46:49.56,Default,,0,400,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}吶  不用了  我自己來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.94,1:46:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去去就來
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.44,1:46:50.75,Default,,400,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}都說了沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.85,1:46:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來一下
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.10,1:46:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.91,1:46:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.03,1:46:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}不要  不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.89,1:46:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.70,1:46:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.13,1:46:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可沒把你當作母親
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.75,1:47:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}是  我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.60,1:47:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想保護你
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.58,1:47:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我保護不了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.65,1:47:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我保護不了你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.08,1:47:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}為什麼  那個人會…如此地珍視我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.18,1:47:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教會我的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.36,1:47:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.90,1:47:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.69,1:47:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾  對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.58,1:47:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.60,1:47:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.57,1:47:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不哭了呢  我可是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.37,1:47:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.83,1:47:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽…要打破約定了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.97,1:47:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.08,1:47:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜歡媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.24,1:47:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.09,1:48:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.69,1:48:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.94,1:48:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.21,1:48:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.93,1:48:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要我還活著
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.51,1:48:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞爾的希比歐就會繼續編織
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.41,1:48:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請不要笑我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.29,1:48:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老看到你這花貓臉肯定也要笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.76,1:48:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定會笑的
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.44,1:49:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你能教會她離別不只是痛苦  她會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.28,1:49:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上車  出發了 
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.32,1:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了邂逅又一段的離別出發
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.86,1:49:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}長老大人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.66,1:49:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.72,1:49:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己愛上艾瑞爾真好
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.40,1:49:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛上他  真好
